 20-COX &HT;    COX NEWS SERVICE THURSDAY COMMENTARY BUDGET
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   These columns for release Thursday, August 20, 1998, are moving
today to clients of the New York Times News Service.
