<P>
   The Framingham Heart Study, based in New England, turns 50 in
September, with two generations now contributing invaluable data on
heart disease, diet and health. One conclusion is that lifestyle
changes are proving hard to make.
</P>
<P>
   Slugged BC-HEART-STUDY-LIFEBEAT-NYTSF, priority code w, category
code l) &QL;
