<HEADLINE>
IN-HNS  
 &HT;    EUROPE 
</HEADLINE>
 CLINTON PREDICAMENT WOULD NOT HAVE HAPPENED News Analysis  
 (For use by New York Times New Service clients)  
 By BERNARD D. KAPLAN  
 c.1998 Hearst Newspapers  
<TEXT>
