<P>
   VENTURE-INVESTORS (Undated) -- As the venture capital market
appears headed for a banner year, investors are flocking to venture
capital funds with good reason. By Chana Schoenberger. 750 words.
</P>
<P>
   MA-HMO-SENIORS (Boston) -- The days of unlimited drug benefits
for seniors may be over. HMOs are planning to cap senior drug
benefits for the first time in January. By Alex Pham.
</P>
<P>
   ONBUSINESS-COLUMN (Undated) _ Boston's MGI Properties survived
the mortgage REIT debacle years ago, but now it's chosen to
liquidate. By Steven Syre and Steve Bailey.
</P>
