and places around the world. So when terrorists simultaneously
bombed U.S. embassies in Kenya and Tanzania on Aug. 7, killing 250
people, including 12 Americans, the company saw it as potential for
growth in government contracts. (Pounds, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
