About 700 of the 724 riders who started in Seattle on June 15
crossed the finish line Aug. 1 in Washington, D.C. Together, we
rode 3,350 miles and raised $6.5 million to aid the American Lung
Association's fight against lung disease. (Reeder, Palm Beach Post)
