<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-19 17:53 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1884 &Cx1f; tad-z
u d &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FOOD-LUNCH-RECIPES-CO     08-19 2900
