</P>
<P>
   Just remember that these figures will only get you in the
ballpark. Homefair cautions site users to do their own tax
calculations. Other decisions you make, from the kind of car you
plan to drive to how you plan to spend your time, will also
influence the amount you'll need.
</P>
<P>
   But even the ballpark figures are pretty darn dramatic. Small
wonder that natives in New Mexico and Colorado complain about
immigrants from California inflating home prices. And small wonder
that the snowbird's path from New York to Florida is so well worn.
</P>
<P>
   A move from Manhattan to Fort Myers will cut your cost of living
by an amazing two-thirds.
</P>
<P>
   Suddenly that Social Security check doesn't look nearly so puny
and impotent.
</P>
<P>
   Note that we're not suggesting that you buy a double-wide
trailer and live downwind of a feed lot in Amarillo. All we're
talking about is downsizing the house or moving to an area of the
country that isn't congested.
</P>
<P>
   It's the one way millions of American have to get rich _ or at
least richer _ quick. &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; (EDITOR'S NOTE: Contributing editor Scott Burns is the
personal-finance columnist for the Dallas Morning News and a
regular columnist for WORTH. His E-mail address is
scott &LR; scottburns.com, and his Web-site address is
www.scottburns.com.) &LR;  &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
