   &UR; LETTERMAN LATE SHOW TOP TEN &LR;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; Heard outside theater showing ``How Stella Got her Groove
Back'' &LR;
</P>
<P>
   10. `I hope I never lose my groove.'
</P>
<P>
   9. `I knew she'd get her groove back, but I couldn't believe how
she her groove back.'
</P>
<P>
   8. `I've seen movies with groove back getting, but that was the
groove back gettingest movie I've ever seen.'
</P>
<P>
   7. `Robin Williams was so funny as the voice of the groove!'
</P>
<P>
   6. `She got her groove back, but I want my nine dollars back.'
</P>
<P>
   5. `This is the exact reason I always write my name inside my
groove.'
</P>
<P>
   4. `What do you mean 'Saving Private Ryan' is sold out?'
</P>
<P>
   3. `Turns out her groove was under the sofa cushion the whole
time.'
</P>
<P>
   2. `Hey, Stella! I got your groove right here!'
</P>
<P>
   1. `Am I the only white guy here?'
</P>
<P>
   &UR; More David Letterman Late Show Top Ten &LR;
