<P>
   LAPD-CHANGES (Los Angeles) _ Seven years after the police
beating of Rodney King sparked a call for widespread reform, Chief
Bernard C. Parks is expected to tell the Police Commission that all
but 20 of the 102 recommendations have been carried out. By Rick
Orlov. (Will move in the ``a'' national and ``n'' California news
files.)
</P>
<P>
   CITYHOOD-PETITION (Los Angeles) _ The state Senate voted 37-0 to
grant a San Fernando Valley petition drive three more months to
trigger a government study of Valley cityhood. By David R. Baker.
(Will move in the ``a'' national and ``n'' California news files.)
</P>
