<HEADLINE>
LAVENDER REVIVAL RESCUES PROVENCAL VILLAGES  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (RESENDING from Aug. 17)   (This interesting 1,000-word ``separate buy'' article is from The
Independent newspaper in London.)  
  
